  "texts": [
    "It was shown that 93% of MSA sentences.",
    "Produced by Elissa were correct.",
    "Elissa was used for pivoting through MSA in a dialect-English MT system, and the BLEU score improved by 0.6 to 1.4%.",
    "In this paper 14 A rule-based method based on a linguistic model was employed to translate the Moroccan dialect into MSA.",
    "The system is based on morphological analysis using the Alkhalil morphological analyzer 15, which has been modified and extended to include Moroccan dialect affixes, as well as a bilingual dictionary (created using situations from television shows and data gathered from the internet)."
  ],
